data.description: This charming home is back on the market due to buyers financing falling through. This home is the perfect combination of comfort and convenience. With a white picket fence and mature trees, it exudes a welcoming atmosphere that will make you feel right at home. Inside, there are 3 cozy bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, providing ample space for you and your family to relax and unwind. One of the best features of this home is its location. It is conveniently situated near major highways, making it easy to get around town. Plus, it is just a short distance away from schools and a variety of restaurants and shops, ensuring that you have everything you need right at your fingertips. This home offers the best of both worlds - a peaceful and comfortable living space in a prime location. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful house your new home!
